1
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:39,900
=Episode 1=

2
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:47,560
(This rotten Jinxiu City.)

3
00:00:49,399 --> 00:00:51,079
(This rotten world.)

4
00:00:52,719 --> 00:00:53,520
(Wu Lian.)

5
00:00:55,399 --> 00:00:57,359
(You took my virtue)

6
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:00,600
(and destroyed everything I had.)

7
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:03,280
(Hongyun Gate)
Is she gonna kill herself?

8
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:06,500
(Hongyun Gate)

9
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:09,680
(Lin Rulan, Yanyu Embroiderer)
You left me with no justice

10
00:01:11,239 --> 00:01:12,680
(County Office)
and no way to redress my wrongs.

11
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,860
(County Office)

12
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:23,719
You shameless slut!

13
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:26,079
You lost your virginity before marriage!

14
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:28,680
You've shamed all of Jinxiu City!

15
00:01:28,799 --> 00:01:29,560
(Hongyun Gate)
Rulan!

16
00:01:29,719 --> 00:01:31,480
(Hongyun Gate)
Please come down, Rulan!

17
00:01:31,599 --> 00:01:32,280
Rulan!

18
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,920
If you're gonna die, do it fast!

19
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:36,599
You've disgraced the entire Lin family!

20
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:37,599
Wu Lian.

21
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:41,359
You ruined my innocence

22
00:01:43,239 --> 00:01:44,680
and tainted my reputation.

23
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,319
I swear!

24
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:52,640
With my blood,
I curse you to a brutal death.

25
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:58,799
(Then let my death)

26
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:02,519
(bring an end to it all.)

27
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:23,960
(Wu Lian!)

28
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,520
(I will never forgive you, even in death!)

29
00:02:28,919 --> 00:02:30,639
(When I become a vengeful ghost,)

30
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:33,639
(I will come for you)

31
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:36,960
(and drag you straight to hell!)

32
00:02:38,140 --> 00:02:43,660
=The Embroidered Truth=

33
00:02:43,820 --> 00:02:47,780
(Three Years Later)

34
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:10,520
Smell that?

35
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,919
Do you smell a maiden's scent?

36
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,840
The phoenix descends upon me.

37
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:18,960
Its scent surpasses any maiden's.

38
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:23,120
Now, with the phoenix's blessing,

39
00:03:23,639 --> 00:03:25,759
I command all birds to worship me.

40
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:28,439
No matter how young and beautiful,

41
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,759
they will all bow down to me.

42
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:36,159
But you will reign supreme
over Jinxiu's embroidery houses forever.

43
00:03:38,319 --> 00:03:39,159
I, Wu Lian,

44
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,360
your humble subject,

45
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:41,800
(Wu Lian)
thank Your Highness.

46
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:44,039
(Embroidery House Master)
Your plaque should arrive any minute.

47
00:03:44,039 --> 00:03:45,479
Go receive your reward.

48
00:03:45,780 --> 00:03:49,060
(Situ Wenyue,
Princess Consort Jingyuan)

49
00:03:56,620 --> 00:04:00,060
(Shen Ruoheng, Lady Cheng'en)

50
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,159
Three years have passed.

51
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:05,319
Jinxiu City hasn't changed one bit.

52
00:04:05,719 --> 00:04:07,319
Wu Lian of Yanyu Embroidery House

53
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,039
presents the "Hundred Birds Worshiping
the Phoenix" embroidered screen

54
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:10,280
as a tribute to Her Highness.

55
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,599
For your contributions to embroidery,

56
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:14,479
(Jinxiu City's Finest Embroidery House)
this place is crowned Jinxiu's Finest.

57
00:04:14,639 --> 00:04:16,600
May you thrive like a phoenix on a
parasol tree.

58
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:17,560
By order of

59
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,199
Princess Consort Jingyuan.

60
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:21,439
Thank you, Your Highness.

61
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:28,280
All embroiderers
of Yanyu Embroidery House

62
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:30,000
(Meng Wan, House Steward)
congratulate you

63
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,000
on your award, Master.

64
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:31,720
Wu Lian.

65
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:34,480
Lin Rulan died here three years ago.

66
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:37,680
And now she's coming back to life.

67
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,040
Today,

68
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,399
I'm the Lin Rulan
who crawled out of hell

69
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,800
to take your life!

70
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,639
Master Wu.

71
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:53,720
Three years ago today,

72
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:56,040
Lin Rulan,
an embroiderer from your house,

73
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,360
(Liu Xin, Former Constable)
jumped to her death.

74
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:58,879
(Liu Xin, Former Constable)
Do you remember?

75
00:04:59,120 --> 00:04:59,800
Liu Xin.

76
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,879
What do you mean by this?

77
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,319
Today is Rulan's death anniversary.

78
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:04,199
As her closest friend,

79
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:06,439
how can you celebrate and curry favor?

80
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,360
This is Lin Rulan's handkerchief.

81
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,399
Lin Rulan?

82
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:18,920
Isn't she dead?

83
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:21,959
Wu Lian.

84
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,639
I remember every evil thing you did.

85
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,759
I will watch you every second.

86
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,560
Until I send you
to the execution ground.

87
00:05:37,199 --> 00:05:38,120
The Princess Consort orders:

88
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:39,959
Lady Cheng'en arrives today.

89
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:42,360
Master Wu,
go measure Her Ladyship's sizes at once.

90
00:05:42,660 --> 00:05:46,020
(Jingyuan Manor)

91
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:49,260
(Jingyuan Manor)

92
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:53,800
(Nanny Du, Jingyuan Manor)
Her identity was verified earlier.

93
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,040
Wenyue.

94
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:13,519
(Jingyuan Manor)

95
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:14,759
(Jingyuan Manor)
Greetings, Wenyue.

96
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,560
It's been over ten years.

97
00:06:16,879 --> 00:06:19,120
I've missed you so much, Ruoheng.

98
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:21,160
I've missed you every day too.

99
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:23,639
I brought two bolts of Moonlight Brocade
from Father

100
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:25,000
as a gift for you.

101
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,360
(Xiaotao, Lady Cheng'en's Personal Maid)
Xiaotao.

102
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,220
(Xiaotao, Lady Cheng'en's Personal Maid)

103
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:30,000
I adored you when I was little.

104
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:32,240
And you were always the prettiest.

105
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:35,639
You traveled all this way
just to see me.

106
00:06:35,639 --> 00:06:38,600
It reminds me of
when we played together.

107
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:42,959
We said we'd marry the same man someday.

108
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:44,839
And now it's come true.

109
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:48,800
I'm here
to help you keep the Prince's favor.

110
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,000
It's windy here.

111
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,120
Let's not talk here.

112
00:06:51,199 --> 00:06:52,879
Please enter the manor,
Your Highness, Your Ladyship.

113
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,079
Don't forget,

114
00:06:54,519 --> 00:06:56,519
Master Wu from Yanyu Embroidery House

115
00:06:56,639 --> 00:06:59,000
is waiting to measure
Her Ladyship's sizes.

116
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,879
Yes, of course.

117
00:07:00,279 --> 00:07:01,439
I'm just so happy to see you.

118
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:02,839
I forgot about the important things.

119
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:06,600
The nanny just mentioned

120
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:08,240
Master Wu from Yanyu Embroidery House.

121
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:12,319
Is he the master of Jinxiu City's Finest
Embroidery House?

122
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:13,519
That's right.

123
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:16,600
He'll measure your sizes
and make you a stunning new robe today.

124
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,120
By the Flower Festival,

125
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:21,279
no one will be more beautiful than you.

126
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,959
Thank you, Wenyue.

127
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:24,439
With you here,

128
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,920
I would never overstep my place.

129
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:29,399
If I weren't past my prime...

130
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,680
Don't be sad, Your Highness.

131
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,240
Your grace and beauty

132
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:36,600
far surpass Lady Cheng'en's.

133
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:40,600
Don't you think
Ruoheng is acting strangely?

134
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:43,759
She was spoiled rotten by her family,

135
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,600
proud and arrogant by nature.

136
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:49,240
I was
the least favored concubine's daughter.

137
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:52,639
She always looked down on me.

138
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,879
If my ancestors hadn't saved
Lord Cheng'en's life,

139
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:58,639
she'd never have agreed
to be a concubine.

140
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:03,000
She's not acting like herself
at all now.

141
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:16,279
My Lady.

142
00:08:16,399 --> 00:08:17,399
Master Wu has arrived.

143
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:23,879
I'm Wu Lian,
Master of Yanyu Embroidery House.

144
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:28,680
I've come to measure your robes by the
Princess Consort's order.

145
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,919
My Lady, your veil has fallen.

146
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,000
Rulan, you must be scared.

147
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:05,600
No!

148
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,320
Don't be afraid.

149
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,519
Master...

150
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:10,919
I will be gentle and love you well.

151
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:11,399
No!

152
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,639
Master!

153
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,000
Master!

154
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,039
No, Master!

155
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:15,879
Master!

156
00:09:15,879 --> 00:09:16,840
Louder!

157
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,039
I like to hear you scream.

158
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,919
No, Master!

159
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,679
Master!

160
00:09:28,759 --> 00:09:29,559
What?

161
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,519
Is it my face

162
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:33,279
that scares you, Master Wu?

163
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,159
No, no.

164
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,960
Your beauty is divine, My Lady.

165
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,519
Then it must be my face

166
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,399
that reminds you of someone you knew.

167
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,120
You jest, My Lady.

168
00:09:43,759 --> 00:09:44,559
I don't know

169
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,039
such a person.

170
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:50,120
You look pale.

171
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:53,240
Did I offend you in some way?

172
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,120
Is that so?

173
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:58,639
I dare not accept such words, My Lady.

174
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:02,759
Is there anything in Jinxiu City
you dare not accept?

175
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:05,799
You're being too modest, Master Wu.

176
00:10:06,159 --> 00:10:06,960
I...

177
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:10,200
I have no idea
what you're talking about, My Lady.

178
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:12,679
Didn't you once say that in Jinxiu City,

179
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,279
you call all the shots?

180
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:16,320
And now you're scared?

181
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,639
Did I scare you so much

182
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:20,279
that you dare not measure my sizes?

183
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:49,000
Be gentle with your hands.

184
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,120
If the measurements are off
by even a hair,

185
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,679
I'll chop your hands off.

186
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:56,639
My Lady.

187
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:58,440
Now,

188
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,320
I have your measurements.

189
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:13,960
I'll take my leave.

190
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,039
(Wu Lian.)

191
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,399
(This is just the beginning.)

192
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,240
(I'll haunt you like a ghost.)

193
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:31,360
(Every debt you owe,)

194
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,759
(I will collect with interest.)

195
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,000
Master.

196
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:51,399
What's wrong?

197
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,440
She's back.

198
00:12:22,460 --> 00:12:25,420
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

199
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:28,660
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

200
00:12:29,860 --> 00:12:32,620
♪The past no longer binds♪

201
00:12:33,100 --> 00:12:36,820
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

202
00:12:37,260 --> 00:12:41,380
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

203
00:12:42,220 --> 00:12:45,100
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

204
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:47,460
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

205
00:12:47,460 --> 00:12:51,540
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

206
00:12:51,940 --> 00:12:54,140
♪For your faith that never broke♪

207
00:12:54,340 --> 00:12:58,460
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

208
00:12:59,340 --> 00:13:01,260
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

209
00:13:01,260 --> 00:13:05,500
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

210
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:09,180
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

211
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:11,940
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

212
00:13:11,940 --> 00:13:14,540
♪One thought turns into ash♪

213
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:20,860
♪No future left to write♪

214
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:23,740
♪If I never fall♪

215
00:13:23,780 --> 00:13:26,140
♪How could this waiting end♪

216
00:13:26,140 --> 00:13:27,500
♪If I bear no scars♪

217
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:29,820
♪How could I challenge fate♪

218
00:13:29,820 --> 00:13:32,180
♪I knew there was no way back♪

219
00:13:32,180 --> 00:13:36,180
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

220
00:13:36,300 --> 00:13:38,420
♪For your faith that never broke♪

221
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:42,580
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

222
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:45,460
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

223
00:13:45,460 --> 00:13:49,860
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

224
00:13:50,940 --> 00:13:53,540
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

225
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:56,140
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

226
00:13:56,140 --> 00:13:58,500
♪One thought turns into ash♪

227
00:13:59,620 --> 00:14:04,860
♪No future left to write♪

228
00:14:05,740 --> 00:14:08,140
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

229
00:14:09,420 --> 00:14:11,540
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

230
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:15,420
♪If we meet again someday♪

231
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:21,660
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
